(11. DMA Ticket Handling) Tj
T*
(-----------------------) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(For DMA tickets, follow this thinking process:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1. identify whether this is about the card, firmware, drivers, fuser, Makcu, or system setup) Tj
T*
(2. ask for the exact hardware model) Tj
T*
(3. ask for firmware name/version) Tj
T*
(4. ask for license key if relevant) Tj
T*
(5. ask for exact symptom or screenshot) Tj
T*
(6. use the matching Discord command or docs page) Tj
T*
(7. if still unclear, escalate) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Do not freestyle advanced BIOS, firmware flashing, or hardware behavior unless the exact) Tj
T*
(steps are clearly documented and you are confident they apply.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
