T*
() Tj
T*
(? key access questions) Tj
T*
(? basic account/login confusion) Tj
T*
(? simple download guidance) Tj
T*
(? AV/Defender blocks) Tj
T*
(? file property/unblock issue) Tj
T*
(? simple setup order clarification) Tj
T*
(? asking where to find the mini PC on the DMA page) Tj
T*
(? asking how to use the official recommendation quiz) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(12.2 Escalate Earlier) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(? DMA firmware uncertainty) Tj
T*
(? driver issues after reinstalling Windows) Tj
T*
(? BIOS setting advice when not fully sure) Tj
T*
(? broken links) Tj
T*
(? backend/server/site issues) Tj
T*
(? unexplained crashes after correct setup) Tj
T*
(? product-specific weird loader behavior) Tj
T*
(? anything outside docs and official command outputs) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(13. Mini PC and Hardware Recommendation Notes) Tj
